{"tid":899946,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"印尼青年水煮用過衛生棉「吸毒」　緝毒官指喝後感「飄飄然」","createTime":"2018-11-13T00:30:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-13T01:50:47.000Z","uid":122,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"92064a2b07d53f9b2cb5adaf365a11ebdd730ceb","tid":899946,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T00:30:26.000Z","msg":"印尼警方日前拘捕一批「吸毒」青年，他們在垃圾桶中翻找用過的衛生棉，並放入水中煮沸，冷卻後再將水一口喝下，聲稱可以替代毒品，得到和吸毒相同的快感，而且更便宜。<br />\n<br />\n據印尼傳媒報道，儘管這聽起來既噁心又不衛生，但印尼國家緝毒局官員Suprinarto表示，煮沸的衛生棉水中含有氯氣，喝下後會產生一股飄飄然、飛起來的幻覺，與服用毒品的感覺相當類似。當地警方已經在首都雅加達、西爪哇和中爪哇等地，拘捕多名以類似方法「吸毒」的青年。<br />\n<br />\n此現象早在2016年出現在印尼西爪哇和邦加勿里洞，自2017年起案例愈來愈多。飲酒安全倡議者吉丁（Jimy Ginting）表示，這種現象日漸普遍，「我不知道是誰帶頭，但目前沒有法律條文能提出起訴，而且現時甚至有青年人，濫用驅蚊劑和咳藥水，藉此得到喝醉的快感。」"},{"pid":"9a53f855809dbc947dd30e63545a476507362844","tid":899946,"uid":57862,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T00:31:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bac4df4923fb57f779c5930672fb79d33b59df3","tid":899946,"uid":44454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T00:33:06.000Z","msg":"少女味的毒品"},{"pid":"912f233618124e79e4de069e6cb3568d8bca99e7","tid":899946,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T00:40:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181112/s00005/1542034896222\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181112%2Fs00005%2F1542034896222&d=SsN2fCzZsuJIJ9cIHCIj4U4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=abc6472e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181112%2Fs00005%2F1542034896222&h=40ba09b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181112/s00005/1542034896222</a>"},{"pid":"d26abb8c51473a6079c2d6a78567b9b1a0c4a1de","tid":899946,"uid":48021,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3